  "title": "Dr Cai Yu Group: Assistant Research Officer",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a highly motivated and committed individual to join our dynamic research team. This project focuses on understanding the reproductive system of Aedes mosquito to advance the development of novel population control strategies. The successful candidate will have the opportunity to lead an independent research component within the project.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>· MSc / BSc (Honors) in Biological Sciences or a related field.<br />· Basic training in cell biology and biochemistry. <br />· Experience in insect genetics is a strong advantage.<br />· Strong motivation and ability to work independently and collaboratively as part of a research team.</p><p>Salary and benefits are commensurable to the educational qualifications and working experience of the candidate. Benefits include annual leave, medical and flexi-benefits, etc.</p><p>Interested individuals should send their applications (including a cover letter, curriculum vitae and two recommendation letters) to:</p><p>Dr CAI Yu<br />Senior Principal Investigator<br />Temasek Life Sciences Laboratory Limited <br />Email: <u>caiyu@tll.org.sg</u><br />(Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified)</p>",
